      "source_path": "delta_swap/faq.md",
      "chunk_index": 0,
      "text": "# Delta Swap FAQ Reward APR is an estimate, not a guarantee. It changes as liquidity depth, trading volume, and incentive emissions change. If two dashboards show different numbers, first check whether one is showing gross APR and the other is showing net APR after fees or incentives. Price speculation is not part of support. For factual updates, check the latest official announcement and the product docs.",
